author: Nathan Allison
reviewBody: I graduated from here in 2009 in Humanities. I went and continued my studies in UCD in 2016 and I preferred Carlow College. The Carlow College lecturers and staff were top notch. They were friendly and helpful. Most knew the students names and the high quality lectures had a relaxed and personal touch. I wasn't mad about living in Carlow but the College was decent.
name: Carlow College, St Patrick's,
